Current local baseline, recorded 2026-07-02:
- Forked Home Assistant custom component for encrypted Samsung TV control.
- Intended local target includes Samsung Orsay TVs, specifically a Samsung UE55H6290.
- Desired functions include HDMI source selection, volume control, and power control.
